    "summary": "Krisp exposes a hosted MCP server at `https://mcp.krisp.ai/mcp` authenticated with OAuth 2.0 + PKCE, plus a REST Portal API for team/admin management at `https://teams.krisp.ai/api/v1` using HTTP Basic auth with a Krisp-issued API key name and secret.",
